it.csi.mddtools.guigen
Interface SecurityModel

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
public interface SecurityModel
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Security Model'. Caratteristiche di sicurezza dell'applicazione

The following features are supported:

  • Autentication Method
  • Actors
  • Use Cases
  • Security App ID
  • Roles
  • User Info Logout Action
  • Ask For Confirmation On Logout

See Also:
GuigenPackage.getSecurityModel()
